thread.title_full: Fall Out Boy Premieres 'Irresistible' Ft. Demi Lovato in Doug the Pug-Starring Video

author: AceShowbiz.com
title: Fall Out Boy Premieres 'Irresistible' Ft. Demi Lovato in Doug the Pug-Starring Video
text:
Comments The remake of the band's 'American Beauty/American Psycho' single was released on the same day as Lovato's new album 'Confident'. 
Fall Out Boy 's collaboration with Demi Lovato is out. Days after being announced, the remake of the band's "Irresistible" landed online on early Friday morning, October 16, the same day the former Disney star's latest album " Confident " officially arrived. The new version hit the web via YouTube along with a music video starring Doug the Pug. The pup is first seen at a basketball court as he reworks some scenes from the original "Irresistible" video . Later, he dons glasses, a wig and a pair of headphones, channeling frontman Patrick Stump , while the vocalist and Lovato are taking turns singing the track. "Irresistible" is featured on FOB's " American Beauty/American Psycho " album that was released earlier this year. When announcing the remake a few days ago, the group praised Lovato, saying she had "one of the most powerful voices today." FOB is currently preparing themselves for their "Wintour Is Coming" tour , which is opening on February 25 and will include 19 other stops in cities across North America.
